               <p>I missed 200 lb. and odd weight of lead off a hot house in Sir James Lowther's garden; I saw it safe the day before. I found the lead at a Mr. Field's, at Staines. We compared it with the place the lead was taken from, and it fitted exactly.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17780115-67-person608">
                  JOSEPH
                   FIELD
