               <p>I laid the lead down on the hot-house; I compared it when it was brought back; it is the same.</p>
               <p>HARPER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I am a <rs id="t17780115-67-deflabel358" type="occupation">bargeman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780115-67-defend602 t17780115-67-deflabel358"></join>; we were fishing in the Thames and found the lead.</p>
               <p>MILL's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I am a <rs id="t17780115-67-deflabel359" type="occupation">fisherman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780115-67-defend604 t17780115-67-deflabel359"></join>; we found the lead in the Thames.</p>
